{"id":2587,"date":"2025-05-13T15:57:19","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:57:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2587"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:21:38","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:21:38","slug":"phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u00ed quy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel: 3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da nhanh l\u00e0nh, gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba peel da v\u00e0 \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n quy tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc, t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn<\/span><\/i><i> serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n <\/i><i>\u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong. C\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay!<\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-%e2%80%93-da-thuong-nhu-the-nao-sau-peel\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel &#8211; Da th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau peel<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Peel da c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? Sau khi peel, da tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y k\u00e9o theo nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2589\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2589\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2589 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-1.webp\" alt=\"Da th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau peel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2589\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau peel<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng, bong tr\u00f3c: Do l\u1edbp s\u1eebng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi suy y\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ecf r\u00e1t, nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: L\u00e0n da m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdi v\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1: N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ef9, da d\u1ec5 s\u1ea1m \u0111en, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00e2m n\u00e1m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i kho\u1ebb m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chi-tiet-cac-giai-doan-phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-hieu-qua-nhat\"><\/span><b>Chi ti\u1ebft c\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Peel da c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? Peel da l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y b\u1ecb sai l\u1ec7ch \u0111i hay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1, bong tr\u00f3c, \u0111au r\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu. H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da sau peel chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-diem-nhay-cam-3-ngay-dau-sau-peel\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: 3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u sau peel<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau peel, l\u00e0n da m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u1edbp s\u1eebng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 n\u00ean d\u1ec5 bong tr\u00f3c, \u1eedng \u0111\u1ecf. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o <\/span><b>c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare sau peel da:<\/b><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2588\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2588\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2588 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-gsc.webp\" alt=\"3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u sau peel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-gsc.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-gsc-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-gsc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-gsc-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2588\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u sau peel<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng: \u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1i sinh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eeda 3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u. GSC \u01b0u ti\u00ean khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 p.H \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng 5-5.5 pH.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng x\u1ecbt kho\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Hyaluronic Acid, B5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec l\u00e0n da n\u00ean c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m b\u1eb1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u d\u00e0nh cho da sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 EGF,&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh n\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i: Kh\u00f4ng b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u00ec da ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e3y che ch\u1eafn b\u1eb1ng m\u0169, k\u00ednh r\u00e2m, kh\u1ea9u trang.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, 3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau peel l\u00e0 l\u00fac da y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: Sau khi peel da n\u00ean d\u00f9ng serum n\u00e0o: G\u1ee3i \u00fd\u00a0 serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da cao c\u1ea5p GSC<\/b><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giai-doan-vang-tai-tao-phuc-hoi-tu-ngay-4-den-ngay-7\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0ng t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o &amp; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i: T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 4 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n <\/span><b>ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1eafm l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c quy t\u1eafc sau \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2590\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2590\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2590 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-gsc.webp\" alt=\"Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0ng t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o &amp; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i: T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 4 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-gsc.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-gsc-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-gsc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-gsc-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2590\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0ng t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o &amp; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i: T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 4 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m: T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9a Peptides, Panthenol, Ceramides.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd (d\u1ea1ng mineral sunscreen) v\u1edbi SPF 30+. V\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da r\u1ea5t m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da treatment, x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 t\u00ednh treatment: Tr\u00e1nh xa AHA, BHA, Retinol, tretinol, adapalen,..hay Vitamin C cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi da \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00eam m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m &amp; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i cho da n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n( \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nh\u01b0 HA, Cica, B5)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duy-tri-duong-da-co-ban-sau-7-ngay\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n: Sau 7 ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n sau 7 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. Khi l\u00e0n da \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng 70\u201380%, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2592\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2592\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2592 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/quy-tac-phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel.webp\" alt=\"Duy tr\u00ec d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n: Sau 7 ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/quy-tac-phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/quy-tac-phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/quy-tac-phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/quy-tac-phuc-hoi-da-sau-peel-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2592\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Duy tr\u00ec d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n: Sau 7 ng\u00e0y<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, Peptides, v\u00e0 Niacinamide, EGF \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da x2: Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i tia UV kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Quan s\u00e1t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng da: Sau khi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m peel m\u1ee5n cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng. N\u1ebfu da c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, h\u00e3y quay l\u1ea1i b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>&gt;&gt;\u00a0 KH\u00c1M PH\u00c1 NGAY: B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau treatment nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3?\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau peel<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi quy tr\u00ecnh khoa h\u1ecdc, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o nhanh, gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n quy tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc, t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong. C\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2591,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[12,8],"class_list":["post-2587","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh","tag-lam-dep-da","tag-new"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2587","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2587"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2587\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3990,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2587\/revisions\/3990"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2591"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2587"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2587"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2587"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}